data.description: New flooring in the bedrooms and fresh paint throughout !Welcome to this charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom ranch-style home, nestled on a spacious lot. This home was recently update in the past few years.As you step inside, the oversized tile flooring guides you through the open concept living area, highlighting the functionality of the space. The kitchen boasts sleek granite countertops, offering both durability and sophistication.This home features a generously-sized laundry room, providing convenience and ample storage options. Moving outdoors, a large fenced-in backyard invites relaxation and recreation, offering privacy and security for family gatherings or peaceful moments.Conveniently situated close to schools and shopping centers. Take a look today.
